imdb.plot outline: A free internet channel dedicated to music, comedy, and puppets hosted by BILL MANSPEAKER, founder of the Grammy Nominated, multi-million selling, Guiness World Record holding band GREEN JELLO. Featuring weekly programs like Witch Kitchen With Brenna Manspeaker, The Pre-Show, WTF News, and the LIVE CALL-IN TALK SHOW; The Talkshow About Nothing hosted by BILL MANSPEAKER.
